            "review_text": "this is a great game in my opinon i love speedrunning it so much and it looks like a lot of fun to play with friends to i only got this game for like 10 bucks i think its deffintly worth it has good graphics settings for lower end pcs like mine i highly recomend it if u have the spare 10 bucks but it can get frustrating at times so if u get frustrated easily the game might make u mad but if ur looking for a fun lil game this is perfect especially  for speedrunning."
