        {
            "review_id": "226211523",
            "steam_id": "76561199875315652",
            "playtime_minutes": 768,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "This game changed my life, Human Fall Flat is a one of a kind game. The silly and stupid physics make this game fun to play with everyone. The creativity in this game has never been seen before. The level designs are so fun yet challenging, with friends its a better and peak experience. The levels are so different and unique from each other and makes for a fun and different experience each time. Whether you're launching yourself in a catapult or being a miniature person, Human Fall Flat is fun. No Brakes Games made this game to be at it's fullest potential, and built it with love and passion. Human Fall Flat has new levels every year and it is a wonderful journey to go on. With Human Fall Flat 2 coming (hopefully) soon, I anticipate how the game will look based on the photos and trailers. The downside is that the fan base feels a bit dead, and I do have a hard time finding lobbies with more than 3 people in them. However I am excited if Human Fall Flat 2 will bring people back. I have over 150 hours combined with my PS5 and Xbox playthroughs. Human Fall Flat is peak, everyone must play it."
        },
